@startuml fredrikhgrelland_data-mesh

actor User

participant "SQLPad" as SQLPad
participant "Presto" as Presto
participant "Hive Metastore" as Hive
participant "MinIO" as MinIO
participant "Consul" as Consul
participant "Nomad" as Nomad

User -> SQLPad: Execute SQL query
activate SQLPad

SQLPad -> Consul: Discover Presto service
Consul --> SQLPad: Presto service details

SQLPad -> Presto: Submit query
activate Presto

Presto -> Consul: Discover Hive Metastore service
Consul --> Presto: Hive Metastore service details

Presto -> Hive: Get schema metadata
activate Hive
Hive --> Presto: Return schema metadata
deactivate Hive

Presto -> Consul: Discover MinIO service
Consul --> Presto: MinIO service details

Presto -> MinIO: Fetch data
activate MinIO
MinIO --> Presto: Return data
deactivate MinIO

Presto --> SQLPad: Query results
deactivate Presto

SQLPad --> User: Display results
deactivate SQLPad

note right of Nomad
  Nomad orchestrates and manages
  all service deployments
end note

@enduml